channel.description:
I am going to make a RS lego video but i didnt know what to do it about. my friend suggested "Do the skill cape emotes" so i made the capes, and here are some of them as i have not made all of them.
SORRY THE IMAGES ARE BIG, I DIDNT RELISE WHEN I UPLOADED THEM
For some questions: No i dont know how to focus camera Yes, lego is good Epic for sure I'm not addicted, or am i? - Rehab for me LoL i am 15, youn enoguh to play lego and runescape, Old enough to deal with the nastines of others...... *points at you*
And also thanks for the good comments. And so yo know how bored i am, there was a power strike and i was sitting at the computer bored as hell with my lego. Also, there are 2 vids on youtube now =) attack and firemaking. - there on the fatefullme channel cause thats my channel. =)
